column4: NSLOCTEXT("[AE9DA58247613ADBBE74A7856A475E62]", "BF70DA644646D14FC3D7E0BD6DD78D23", "You are an Ogremon bandit! This is your hideout!")
NSLOCTEXT("[AE9DA58247613ADBBE74A7856A475E62]", "14D50AF54A76D38B136F5783B1332333", "You were lucky last time! Give up!")
NSLOCTEXT("[AE9DA58247613ADBBE74A7856A475E62]", "E5F3C2C34EDB0C9D2DB04281CF3B2020", "I have done nothing wrong. Don\'t come in my house without permission!")
NSLOCTEXT("[AE9DA58247613ADBBE74A7856A475E62]", "E48E4D1A4551741904D9F5896BD18FE8", "You tricked me last time, but now I\'ll get you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[AE9DA58247613ADBBE74A7856A475E62]", "7D3880B741C78085A706C6948F23C3BA", "You want a piece of me? I\'ll knock you out!")
